text.tspan: Users of simulation codes often wish to extend
simulations to include phenomena solved in
OpenFOAM. Such problems appear in cooling
devices, on flexible wings, or even in nuclear fusion
users to quickly couple OpenFOAM to arbitrary
other codes, bridging their communities, and opening
peer-to-peer (without a server): MUI, OpenPALM, preCICE [11,12,2]
